Title: A-Sword-ed Needs
Description:
Swords!

Sorry, I saw you and I did not want to forget.

Yes. We need swords. In the Dream. You can provide, yes?

Please deliver them to Cylania.
ObjectivesText: Deliver 3 Draconium Swords to Cylania in the Emerald Dream

Objectives.Text: Complete the events of "Enter the Dream"
